  "text": "A mesh size of 0.15 × 0.15 mm was used for the parts that were adaptively remeshed as well as for the remaining parts in order to reduce contact problems. Such defined parameters of mesh reconstruction enabled a stable solution of the issue in each computation step [CITATION_1] .",
